cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with deep learning-based segmentation of MRI scans, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The use of Bayesian methods is also relevant to these sub-categories. Finally, the proposed method has potential applications in medical imaging (cs.MM).
